snippet.title: Miya's Everyday Joy of Cooking Trailer
snippet.description: Miya's Everyday Joy of Cooking is a relaxing mobile game full of "mouth-watering, hand-drawn illustrations of all your favorite Korean food like kimchi stew, lettuce wraps, crab croquette, and handmade noodles". Available on the App Store and Google Play.
